  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/81147b25e496b3e081f1e7f8872391d6.webp?t=1764787863\" width=360 height=40 /></span><br>Are we truly evolving.. or just surviving?<br>Is the path we’ve chosen as a species the right one… or a dead end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Exodus Project</i> was meant to reshape us, to build a stronger, better world.<br>To create superhumans.<br>To save us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But something went wrong.<br>Terribly wrong.<br>And now, what was meant to save us is tearing us apart.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Radiant Exodus</strong> is a linear action-horror shooter about loss, survival, and the will to fight back. <br>You play as Sarah Caldwell, a former soldier trying to reconnect with a friend .. but the night has other plans. The city slips into darkness. People disappear. Blood paints the sidewalks. And something.. looms in the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her father might be in danger. The world feels like it’s ending. All she has is an old rifle, her training, and a promise she’s not willing to break.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t just survival. It’s a last stand. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight, linear campaign</strong> : No filler. Just raw action, eerie tension, and story-driven progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cinematic atmosphere</strong> : Dynamic lighting, haunting environments, and a world falling apart around you.. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival-focused combat</strong> : Manage your ammo, stay alert, and face off against twisted, relentless enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unfold a mystery</strong> : Uncover fragments of a hidden truth through notes, transmissions, and moments of quiet dread.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/81147b25e496b3e081f1e7f8872391d6.webp?t=1764787863\" width=360 height=40 /></span><br>Are we truly evolving.. or just surviving?<br>Is the path we’ve chosen as a species the right one… or a dead end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Exodus Project</i> was meant to reshape us, to build a stronger, better world.<br>To create superhumans.<br>To save us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But something went wrong.<br>Terribly wrong.<br>And now, what was meant to save us is tearing us apart.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/880dfc3121e9f2bd1409167fa56dd03c.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Radiant Exodus</strong> is a linear action-horror shooter about loss, survival, and the will to fight back. <br>You play as Sarah Caldwell, a former soldier trying to reconnect with a friend .. but the night has other plans. The city slips into darkness. People disappear. Blood paints the sidewalks. And something.. looms in the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her father might be in danger. The world feels like it’s ending. All she has is an old rifle, her training, and a promise she’s not willing to break.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t just survival. It’s a last stand. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/0aac7be97599a8f9e007fa5951ffcbbd.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight, linear campaign</strong> : No filler. Just raw action, eerie tension, and story-driven progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cinematic atmosphere</strong> : Dynamic lighting, haunting environments, and a world falling apart around you.. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.poster.avif?t=1764787863\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.webm?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/9aac97d59942ad0d35dee56aa113bf2f.mp4?t=1764787863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival-focused combat</strong> : Manage your ammo, stay alert, and face off against twisted, relentless enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unfold a mystery</strong> : Uncover fragments of a hidden truth through notes, transmissions, and moments of quiet dread.</p></li></ul>",
